   Release Information:

   Beach Volleyball: Slap on the sun block and head to the beach for this
   game! 8 Exotic locations from Brazil to Japan. 32 male and 32 female teams    from around the world. Smooth animated moves and stunning 3D graphics.    Multiplayer mode.

   Beach Soccer: Set for its first appearance in 2008 at the Olympics, try
   out this great sport game! 8 great world locations, 320 unique players
   from 32 international teams, golden goal and penalty shoot-outs,
   multiplayer mode.

   Body Boarding: Ride the waves 360 degrees with Mike Stewart, as you hit
   the surf in locations such as Hawaii and Tahiti!! 8 Characters, with
   hidden bonus characters as well plus 8 different body boards to choose
   from. With 15 tricks to master, the 3D effects of waves, water splashing
   ripples and spray means to will almost smell the sea!!

   5-a-Side Football: Head down to the park for some great football fun!!
   32 teams with unique players, eight different locations, with spectacular
   3D motion capturing.

   Scooter Challenge: From Trafalgar Square in London to the Olympic stadium
   in Berlin, race your scooter in exciting world wide locations!! With
   training, single race and championship modes, and a variety of weather
   conditions, and multiplayer action.
